    <item>
      <title>印度正在回归俄罗斯石油</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/business/india-russian-oil.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度与特朗普总统的贸易协议本应停止从俄罗斯进口石油。但随后中东冲突切断了替代供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/business/india-russian-oil.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 05:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普宣布用俄克拉荷马州参议员取代诺姆</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/kristi-noem-markwayne-mullin-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在诺姆在国会听证会上遭到共和党人的质询后，总统表示，他将用参议员马克韦恩·穆林(Markwayne Mullin)取代国土安全部长克里斯蒂·诺姆(Kristi Noem)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/kristi-noem-markwayne-mullin-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 05:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普击败普京，俄罗斯的全球影响力受到削弱</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/world/europe/russia-iran-putin.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗冲突可能会给莫斯科和乌克兰的经济带来短期推动。但这也显示了俄罗斯伙伴关系的局限性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/world/europe/russia-iran-putin.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 05:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>时间表：克里斯蒂·诺姆作为特朗普国土安全部部长的兴衰</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/kristi-noem-dhs-timeline.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四被特朗普总统解雇的国土安全部长帮助履行了他的边境承诺，但也引起了对其政府的负面关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/kristi-noem-dhs-timeline.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 03:56:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与委内瑞拉恢复外交关系</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/world/americas/us-venezuela-diplomatic-relations.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自两个月前抓获委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗以来，华盛顿迅速升温了与委内瑞拉的关系，并对其施加了巨大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/world/americas/us-venezuela-diplomatic-relations.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 03:21:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部公布了爱泼斯坦档案中对特朗普提出指控的女性失踪的采访</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/trump-epstein-interviews-woman-justice-department.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这些页面在与被定罪的性犯罪者杰弗里·爱泼斯坦有关的大量文件中被扣留，因为官员们称错误地判定这些文件是重复的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/trump-epstein-interviews-woman-justice-department.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 01:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员布卢门撒尔推动调查克里斯蒂·诺姆的伪证罪</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/noem-perjury-investigation-blumenthal.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康涅狄格州参议员理查德·布卢门撒尔表示，民主党有证据表明克里斯蒂·诺姆在周二的参议院听证会上宣誓撒谎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/noem-perjury-investigation-blumenthal.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 00:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析表明学校在美国袭击伊朗海军基地时遭到袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/world/middleeast/iran-school-us-strikes-naval-base.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2 月 28 日米纳布的学校罢课造成包括儿童在内的数十人死亡，这似乎是对伊朗南部邻近海军基地发动袭击的一部分，官员称美军正在该基地开展行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/world/middleeast/iran-school-us-strikes-naval-base.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 23:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当诺姆在纳什维尔讲话时，参议院蜂拥而至穆林</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/trump-fires-noem-gop-split-mullin.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这一引人注目的分屏凸显了克里斯蒂·诺姆(Kristi Noem)国土安全部长职务的被罢免是多么突然，即使按照特朗普总统快节奏的华盛顿标准来看也是如此。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/trump-fires-noem-gop-split-mullin.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 21:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林赛·哈利根 (Lindsey Halligan) 正在接受佛罗里达州律师协会的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/lindsey-halligan-investigation-florida-bar.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈利根女士作为一名美国检察官，对特朗普总统的敌人提起了刑事诉讼，她的行为正在接受授权她执业的组织的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/05/us/politics/lindsey-halligan-investigation-florida-bar.html</guid>
